cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a deep image generation neural network to synthesize clothing and uses Web photos to train a fashionability model. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with image generation and manipulation. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses a neural network to learn per-garment encodings and develop an activation maximization-style approach. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is relevant as the paper deals with generating and editing images of clothing. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper evaluates the success of the edits according to human opinion.
